casebody.data:
Mary Katherine DAY-PETRANO, Petitioner
v.
Charles D. HALL, et al. No. 19-5372 Supreme Court of the United States. October 7, 2019

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the District Court of Appeal of Florida, First District dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
